OL,3,CTameside man first in UK to get life-
OL,4,Csaving drug for rare blood disorder
OL,6,FGranada Reports Correspondant Tim
OL,7,FScott has been speaking to David Cope
OL,8,Fabout the new lifesaving drug
OL,10,FA grandfather from Tameside who was
OL,11,Ftreated at Liverpool University
OL,12,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust (LUHFT)
OL,13,Fhas become the first person in the UK
OL,14,Fto be given a new lifesaving drug as
OL,15,Fpart of a clinical trial.
