OL,3,CTameside man first in UK to get life-
OL,4,Csaving drug for rare blood disorder
OL,6,FAfter falling critically ill, David
OL,7,FCope, 67, from Tameside in Manchester,
OL,8,Fwas transported by blue-light
OL,9,Fambulance to the Intensive Care Unit
OL,10,F(ICU) at the Royal Liverpool
OL,11,FUniversity Hospital. After being
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with Thrombotic
OL,13,Fthrombocytopenic purpura (TTP), David
OL,14,Fwent into multiple organ failure and
OL,15,Fwas even placed on life-support to
OL,16,Fhelp his organs recover.
