OL,3,CTameside man first in UK to get life-
OL,4,Csaving drug for rare blood disorder
OL,6,FTTP is a very rare condition that only
OL,7,Faffects 6 in one million people. It
OL,8,Fcauses blood to clot in small blood
OL,9,Fvessels throughout the body, stopping
OL,10,Fblood flow to major organs.
OL,12,FDavid agreed to be put on a drug-trial
OL,13,Fwhich offers a new way to treat TTP.
