OL,3,CTameside man first in UK to get life-
OL,4,Csaving drug for rare blood disorder
OL,6,FLUHFT is the largest TTP Specialist
OL,7,FCentre in the country, running an
OL,8,Finternational clinical research trial,
OL,9,Fwhich offers an alternative treatment
OL,10,Ffor TTP, a life-threatening illness.
OL,11,FCurrent treatment options for TTP can
OL,12,Fbe a very invasive with a long
OL,13,Frecovery time, and this trial aims to
OL,14,Freduce the severity of this treatment
OL,15,Fand continue to improve the patient's
OL,16,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
