OL,3,CTameside man first in UK to get life-
OL,4,Csaving drug for rare blood disorder
OL,6,FDue to the research happening at
OL,7,FLUHFT, David is now back home with his
OL,8,Ffamily. TTP is a life-long condition
OL,9,Fhowever, through research and new
OL,10,Ftreatments, clinicians hope to find
OL,11,Fways to reduce the severity of
OL,12,Ftreatment and the number of flare-ups
OL,13,Fa patient will have in their lifetime.
